headline: Best Buy, Wayfair added to positive catalyst watch at JPMorgan
summary: Investing.com -- JPMorgan has added Best Buy (NYSE:BBY) and Wayfair (NYSE:W) to its Positive Catalyst Watch, citing improving sales trends, attractive valuations, and tariff-related risk that appears more manageable than feared.
